But humans! Here! How did you get here? I want to hear all about it! Of course, I'm not too surprised.
The Creator must have brought you from the future. Your future, I mean. The Creator doesn't have a future. He invented time.
I wonder if the Creator might let us enter your time once in a while so that we can go help you on Earth. How is Earth?
Gabe! I'm glad you're safe and I know you're interested in the humans, but now's not the time for a chat.
We have to get them to the courtyard.
Oh, yes, of course. To the courtyard! We can all talk later. I have so many questions for you.
What is Earth like? Why didn't Adam come with you? The Creator has been telling us about the one He's going to call Adam.
Haha! I am going on. Okay. One more thing. I can teach you a skill before we go: Inspire
Inspire will give you or your Allies the energy to use special skills.
Something about you really inspires me! Get it? Because you learned Inspire!
